Perquisites:
Project depend on sinatra web server and rbovirt, you need to add this commands:
$ sudo yum install ruby-devel rubygems
$ gem install sinatra rbovirt nokogiri
$ bundle install

Note:
if you have problems with development resources try to add that packages:
$ yum install rubygems gcc-c++ libxml libxslt libxslt-devel

Configure the server host and port as well as the oVirt url in:
ovirt.conf.yml configuration file

To run the server:
$ ./webhandler.rb
